OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrance bans short-haul     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fflights to cut CO2         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, France has banned domestic short-haul  
OL,6, flights where train alternatives exist,
OL,7, in a bid to cut carbon emissions.      
OL,9,FThe law came into force two years after
OL,10,Flawmakers had voted to end routes where
OL,11,Fthe same journey could be made by train
OL,12,Fin under two-and-a-half hours.         
OL,14,FThe ban all but rules out air travel   
OL,15,Fbetween Paris and cities including     
OL,16,FNantes, Lyon and Bordeaux, while       
OL,17,Fconnecting flights are unaffected.     
OL,19,FCritics have described the latest      
OL,20,Fmeasures as "symbolic bans".           
